flowchart TD
    A[Customer or Owner on WhatsApp] --> B[Baileys Bot Session Manager]
    B --> C[Bot Router and Command Handling]
    C --> D{Message Type}

    D -->|Owner command| E[Owner Command Handlers]
    E --> F[Convex Queries and Mutations]
    F --> G[(Convex DB + Vector Index + Storage Metadata)]

    D -->|Customer product inquiry| H[RAG Pipeline]
    H --> I[Embeddings + Vector Search]
    I --> G
    H --> J[Prompt Builder with Grounding Context]
    J --> K[AI Provider Manager]
    K --> L[DeepSeek primary]
    K --> M[Gemini fallback]
    K --> N[Groq or other fallback]
    L --> O[Structured AI Response]
    M --> O
    N --> O

    O --> P{Action Type}
    P -->|Respond| Q[Send WhatsApp Reply]
    P -->|Send catalog/images| R[Product and Media Services]
    R --> S[Cloudflare R2 Signed URLs]
    S --> Q
    P -->|Handoff| T[Mute Bot + Notify Owner]
    T --> Q

    D -->|REST API request| U[Hono API]
    U --> V[Auth + Validation + Rate Limit]
    V --> W[Service Layer]
    W --> F
    W --> S

    Q --> X[Conversation and Analytics Events]
    X --> F

    Y[CLI Seed and Backup] --> F
    Z[Web App] --> U
